  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u00a0 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 05 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "05 more people lost their lives due to corona infection in the country",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Yesterday (28.07.2022) 05 more people died due to corona infection in the country, the Government Information Department said.",
        "In that way, five people have died including one male in the age group of 30 to 59 years, three males and one female among those above 60 years of age.",
        "Also, till today (29.07.2022) a total of 665379 people have been affected by corona infection, 143 people have been confirmed to be infected with corona virus today.",
        "It is noteworthy that 665522 people have been diagnosed with corona infection in the country so far."
      ],
